::Perndabot::

Perndabot looks ahead, seeing the shoreline in the distance. It would
be some time before they got there, and even more time before getting
to Alliance island.

"So, where are you from?" he asks Antagony, deciding that they might
as well talk while flying.

jetpack

her 
> special abilities. Antagony silently followed behing Perndabot and
carefully
